{"tid":1313586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班垃圾廢老再咁多嗲就同文宣社會信用評分出去 唔洗等2047 2020年一齊攬炒","createTime":"2019-07-13T21:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T02:06:05.000Z","uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f0df1e3a127af5598f234d3c7e070a9f9af06e0","tid":1313586,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T21:54:45.000Z","msg":"1新聞話三年內將會引進社會信用體系<br />\n但係要注意<br />\n佢個三年係由<span style=\"color: red;\">2018年</span>開始計<br />\n廣東印發推進粵港澳大灣區建設三年行動計劃（2018-2020年）<br />\n所以係出年就已經燒到你肉都無<br />\n2022年？天真少陣<br />\n佢個計劃第75條<br />\n75.<span style=\"color: red;\">加快社會信用體系和市場監管體系建設。</span>研究制定廣東省社會信用條例。探索依法對大灣區內企業聯動實施信用激勵和失信懲戒。建成全省統一的市場監管信息平台。 <br />\n基本上係一定推硬<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gd.gov.cn/gdywdt/gdyw/content/post_2530521.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gd.gov.cn%2Fgdywdt%2Fgdyw%2Fcontent%2Fpost_2530521.html&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULwaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=37b12334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gd.gov.cn/gdywdt/gdyw/content/post_2530521.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聶德權只係出口術，官方文件白字黑字仲留係度</span><br />\n仲想靜靜雞刪左佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/351611/大灣區建-社會信用體系-惹質疑-中央官網刪去港澳台選項\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F351611%2F%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%BB%BA-%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%AB%94%E7%B3%BB-%E6%83%B9%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2%E5%88%AA%E5%8E%BB%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%85&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULwaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=7a09ad19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/351611/大灣區建-社會信用體系-惹質疑-中央官網刪去港澳台選項</a><br />\n<br />\n2 BBC曾經訪問過負責評分既「芝麻信用」關於評分標準，但係對家<span style=\"color: red;\">拒絕訪問</span><br />\n即係話呢個SYSTEM係無透明度可言，佢鐘意扣就扣，鐘意加就加<br />\n同埋，佢係屬於連坐法<br />\n一人扣分，全家攬炒，就連同佢傾計既FD同鄰居一樣中招<br />\n抄家滅族唔係問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://monthly.hkej.com/monthly/article/id/2187426/社會信用系統來襲+你值多少分？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmonthly.hkej.com%2Fmonthly%2Farticle%2Fid%2F2187426%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%B2%2B%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%BC%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E5%88%86%EF%BC%9F&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULwaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=fdf318ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://monthly.hkej.com/monthly/article/id/2187426/社會信用系統來襲+你值多少分？</a><br />\n<br />\n3  你以為乜都唔做就唔會燒埋你上身？<br />\n根據中共對付新疆政府，佢地將36種人士列為「可疑人物」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2777233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2777233&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULwaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=cf71cd27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2777233&h=b5431be7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2777233</a><br />\n特別有幾個香港人一定中招<br />\n<em>7 從海外回國</em> <br />\n<em>16突然變賣所有資產並且無明顯理由移居，尤其是整個家庭一起遷居</em><br />\n<em>17電力使用量不正常</em><br />\n<em>18違反計劃生育政策並擁有多於規定的孩子的人</em> （即係唔可以生多過兩件）<br />\n<em>19 懂得焊接及製造炸彈</em><br />\n<em>21 申請到海外</em><br />\n<em>34 跟「於海外的人」及「被特別監察的人」有關</em><br />\n上面係文宣組翻譯左，而家整緊文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n社會信用體系係雙面刃，本身係大陸已經有好大爭議性<br />\n個SYSTEM本身就係計時炸彈，分分鐘拉埋隔離澳門同成個大陸一齊爆<br />\n（因為賭博都會扣分）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果班廢老黑警同奶共有心阻住香港前進既<br />\n至少我絕對唔介意拖哂成個香港一齊攬炒<br />\n出年就逼佢推呢個SYSTEM<br />\n文宣圖我會越整越多 多到最好要全世界知道真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ee341b580426f2840c992152c05e9eb614512001","tid":1313586,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T22:04:01.000Z","msg":"前幾日寫左信俾總統<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1O8KnvD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1O8KnvD.png&h=820bc140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家只係開始既